hadiths[84]{hadithnumber,text}:
3568,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki, Abdullah-bin-Abu-Bakar se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Umra se riwayat ki, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahaan tashrif farma they unhon (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne aik aadmi ki awaz suni jo Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein dakhil honey ki ijazat maang raha tha. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! ye aadmi aap ke ghar mein dakhil honey ki ijazat maang raha hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mera khayal hai wo falan hai. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik chacha ke barey mein) farmaya ( . padhi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! agar fulaan. padhi. unhon-ne apne aik dudh-sharik chacha ke barey mein kaha, padhi. zinda hota to wo mere ghar mein aa sakta tha? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya : haan , bila shubah razaat (doodh pilaana) un tamam rishton ko haram kar deti hai. jinko wilaadat haram karti hai."
3569,"Hisham-bin-Urwa ne Abdullah-bin-Abu-Bakar se, unhon-ne Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : razaat (doodh pilaaney) se wo (rishtey) haram ho jatey hain. jo wilaadat se haram hotey hain."
3570,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Abu-Bakar ne isi sanad se Hisham-bin-Urwa ki hadis ki tarah khabar di."
3571,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne un (Urwa) ko khabar di ke pardey ke ehkaam nazil honey ke baad abu-Qaees ke bhai Aflah aaey, wo andar aaney ki ijazat chahtey they, aur wo unke dudh-sharik chacha (lagtey) they. unhon-ne kaha : maine unhein ijazat deney se inkar kar diya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to jo maine kiya aapko bataya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke unhein apne samney aaney ki ijazat dun."
3572,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere paas mere dudh-sharik chacha Aflah-bin-abi-Qaees aaey, ( aagey (Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ki hadis ke ham mana bayan kiya aur ye izafa kiya : ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ( maine kaha : mujhey to aurat ne doodh pilaya hai, mard ne nahi pilaya . aap ne farmaya : terey donon hath ya tera dayan hath khaak aalud ho."
3573,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Urwa se riwayat ki, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke pardey ka hukm nazil honey ke baad abu-Qaees ke bhai Aflah aaey, wo unke paas ( ghar ke andar ( aaney ki ijazat chahtey they. abu-Qaees Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik walid they. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main Aflah ko ijazat nahi dun gii yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat ley loon. mujhey abu-Qaees ne to doodh nahi pilaya (ke uska bhai mera mehram bin jaey) mujhey to unki biwi ne doodh pilaya tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaey, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! abu-Qaees ke bhai Aflah mere paas aaey they, wo andar aaney ki ijazat maang rahe they, mujhey achchha na laga ke main unhein ijazat dun yahan tak ke aap se ijazat ley loon. ( Urwa ne) kaha : Hazrat ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhein ijazat de diya karo. Urwa ne kaha : usi ( hukm ( ki wjah se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kaha karti thin : razaat (doodh pilaney) ki wjah se wo sab rishtey haram thehra lo jinhein tum nasb ki wjah se haram thehratey ho."
3574,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se isi sanad ke sath khabar di ke abu-Qaees ke bhai Aflah aaey, wo unke paas ghar ke andar aaney ki ijazat chahtey they. un sab ki hadis ki tarah . padhi. aur is mein hai : wo tumharey chacha hain, tumhara dayan hath khaak aalud ho aur abu-Qaees us aurat ke shauhar they jisne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko doodh pilaya tha."
3575,"ibne-Numair ne Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa-bin-Zubair ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere dudh-sharik chacha aaey, wo mujh se ( ghar ke) andar aaney ki ijazat chahtey they, maine unhein ijazat deney se inkar kar diya yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat ley loon. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine kaha : mere dudh-sharik chacha ne mere paas ( ghar ke andar ( aaney ki ijazat mangi to maine unhein ijazat deney se inkar kar diya. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey chacha tumharey paas (ghar mein) aa jaaein. maine kaha : mujhey aurat ne doodh pilaya tha, mard ne nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo tumharey chacha hain, wo tumharey ghar mein aa saktey hain."
3576,"Hammad, yani ibne-zaid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hisham ne isi sanad se hadis bayan ki ke abu-Qaees ke bhai ne un (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (ke yahan aaney ki ijazat mangi . aagey isi tarah bayan kya."
3577,abu-Muawia ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath isi ki tarah hadis bayan ki magar unhon-ne kaha : abu-Qaees ne unke yahan aaney ki ijazat mangi.
3578,"Ata se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di, kaha : mere dudh-sharik chacha abul-Jaad ne mere paas aaney ki ijazat mangi to maine unhein inkar kar diya. Hisham ne mujh se kaha : ye abu-Qaees hi they. phir jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine aapko ye baat batai. aap ne farmaya : tum ne unhein ijazat kyon na di? tumhara dayan hath ya tumhara hath khaak aalud ho."
3579,"Yazeed bin abi Habib ne Irak (bin Malik Ghifari) se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne usey khabar di ke unke dudh-sharik chacha ne, jinka naam Aflah tha, unke yahan aaney ki ijazat mangi to unhon-ne unke aagey parda kya (unhein rok diya) iske baad unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya to aap ne farmaya : tum unse parda na karo kyonke razaat se bhi wo sab rishtey haram ho jatey hain jo nasb se haram hotey hain."
3580,"Hakam ne Irak bin Malik se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Qaees ke betey Aflah ne mere yahan aaney ki ijazat mangi to maine unhein ijazat deney se inkar kar diya, unhon-ne paigham bheja : main aap ka chacha hon, mere bhai ki biwi ne aapko doodh pilaya hai, is par bhi maine unhein ijazat deney se inkar kar diya, iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney us waqiey ka zikr kya, aap ne farmaya : wo tumharey samney aa sakta hai wo tumhara chacha hai."
3581,"abu-Muawia ne hamein Aamash se khabar di, unhon-ne Sad bin Ubeda se, unhon-ne abu-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! kya wjah hai aap (nikah ke liye) Quraish (ki aurton) ke intikhab ka ehtimam kartey hain aur hamein (banu-Haashim ko) chhod detey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : tumharey paas koi cheez (rishta) hai? maine kaha : ji haan, Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo mere liye halal nahi (kyonke) wo mere doodh-sharik bhai ki beti hai."
3582,"Jareer, Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Sufiyan sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
3583,"Hammam ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Qatada ne Jaabir bin Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti (ke sath nikah karne) ke barey mein khahish ka izhar kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo mere liye halal nahi kyonke wo mere doodh-sharik bhai ki beti hai aur razaat se wo sab rishtey haram ho jatey hain jo raham (wiladat aur nasb) se haram hotey hain."
3584,"Yahya qattaan aur Bishr-bin-Umar ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, Shoba aur Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba donon ne Qatada se Hammam ki (pichhli) sanad ke sath bilkul isi tarah riwayat ki, magar Shoba ki hadis Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qaul : mere dudh-sharik bhai ki beti hai par khatm ho gaee aur Saeed ki hadis mein hai : razaat se wo rishtey haram ho jatey hain jo nasb se haram hotey hain. aur Bishr-bin-Umar ki riwayat main (Jaabir bin Zaid se riwayat hai ki bajaey ye) hai : maine Jaabir bin Zaid se suna."
3585,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : Allah ke rasool! aap Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti (ke sath nikah karne) se (door ya qareeb ( kahan hain? ya kaha gaya : kya aap Hamza bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ko nikah ka paigham nahi bhejengey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Hamza razaat ki bina par yaqeeni taur par mere bhai hain.
3586,"abu-Usama ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hisham ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey mere walid ( Urwa-bin-Zubair ( ne Zainab-binte-abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Umme-Habiba-binte-abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laaey, maine aap se kaha : kya aap meri behan ( azzah ( binte-Abu-Sufiyan ke barey mein koi soch rakhtey hain? aap ne puchha : main kya karun? maine kaha : aap us se nikah kar lein, aap ne farmaya : kya tum is baat ko pasand karti ho? maine kaha : main akelii hi aap ki biwi nahi hun aur apne sath khair mein Sharik honey (ke mamley ( main ( mere liye) sabse zyada mahboob meri behan hai. aap ne farmaya : wo mere liye halal nahi hai. maine kaha : mujhey khabar di gaee hai ke aap durra-binte-abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye nikah ka paigham bhej rahe hain. aap ne puchha : Umme-Salma ki beti ke liye? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne farmaya : agar wo meri god mein na palii hoti to bhi mere liye halal na thi, wo mere dudh-sharik bhai ki beti hai, mujhey aur uske walid ko soobiya ne doodh pilaya tha, isliye tum khawaateen mere samney apni betiyon aur bahnon ke barey mein pesh kash! na kiya karo."
3587,Yahya-bin-Zakariiyaa-bin-abi-Zayda aur Zuhair donon ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath bilkul isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
3588,"Yazeed-bin-abu-Habeeb se riwayat hai ke Muhammad-bin-shahaab (Zohri ( ne (unki taraf ( ye bayan kartey huey likha ke Urwa ne unhein hadis sunai, Zainab-binte-abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse bayan kiya, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz ki, aey Allah ke rasool ! meri behan azzah se nikah kar lijiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya tum ye pasand karo gii? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan , Allah ke rasool ! main akelii aap ki biwi to hon nahi, aur (mujhey ( sabse zyada mahboob , jo khair mein mere sath Sharik ho, meri behan hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo mere liye halal nahi hai. unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! ham se ye baat ki jati hai ke aap darra-binte-abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah karna chahtey hain. aap ne puchha : kya abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti se? unhon-ne jawab diya : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo meri god ki parwarda ( rubaiba ( na hoti to bhi mere liye halal na thi, wo mere dudh-sharik bhai ki beti hai, mujhey aur uske walid abu-Salma ko soobiya ne doodh pilaya tha, isliye tum mujhey apni betiyon aur bahnon (ke sath nikah ( ki pesh kaash! ! na kiya karo."
3589,Aqeel-bin-Khalid aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Muslim donon ne Zohri se ibne-abi Habib ki (pichhli (sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki aur Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib ke siwa unmein se kisi ne apni hadis mein azzeh ( binte-abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu)) ka naam nahi liya.
3590,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Suwed-bin-Saeed ne, apni-apni sanadon se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. Suwed aur Zuhair ne kaha : be-shak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. : ( doodh ki) aik ya do chuskiyaan hurmat ka sabab nahi bantiin."
3591,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , Amr Naaqid aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim sab ne Moatamir se hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Yahya ke hain. padhi. kaha : hamein Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman ne Ayub se khabar di, wo abu-Khaleel se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-Haaris se, unhon-ne umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik dehati Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke aap mere ghar mein tashrif farma they. usne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! (pahley ( meri aik biwi thi, is par maine dusri se shadi kar li, meri pehli biwi ka khayal hai ke usne meri nai biwi ko aik ya do martaba doodh pilaya tha. to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik do martaba doodh dena ( rishtey ko) haram nahi karta. Amr ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Abdullaah-bin-Haaris-bin-naufal se riwayat hai) Abdullah ke walid ke sath dada ka naam bhi liya)."
3592,"Hisham ne mujhey Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Khaleel Saleh bin abi Maryam se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se aur unhon-ne umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke banu-Aamir bin Sasa ke aik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! kya aik martaba doodh peenaa rishton ko haram kar deta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi."
3593,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Abdullah-bin-Haaris se riwayat ki ke umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik ya 2 martaba doodh peena ya aik-do martaba doodh choosna hurmat ka sabab nahi banta."
3594,abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim donon ne Abda bin Sulaiman se aur unhon-ne ibne- abu Aruba se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki lekin Ishaq ne ibne-Bishr ki riwayat ki tarah kaha : ya 2 martaba doodh peena ya 2 martaba doodh choosna aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ne kaha : aur 2 martaba doodh peena aur 2 martaba doodh choosna.
3595,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Qatada se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : aik 2 martaba doodh dena hurmat ka sabab nahi banta."
3596,"Hammam ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Qatada ne baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya : kya aik martaba doodh choosna ( rishtey ko) haram kar deta hai? to aap ne jawab diya : nahi."
3597,"Abdullah-bin-Ubai bakra ne Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Quran mein nazil kya gaya tha ke das baar doodh pilana jinka ilm ho, hurmat ka sabab bin jata hai, phir unhein panch baar doodh pilaaney (ke hukm) se jinka ilm ho, mansukh kar diya gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) faut huey to ye un aayatein mein thi jinki (naskh ka hukm na jaanney waley kuchh logon ki taraf se) Quran mein tilawat ki jati thi."
3598,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Umra se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna. padhi. wo us razaat ka zikr kar rahi thin jis se hurmat Sabit hoti hai. Umra ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Quran mein das baar doodh pilaaney se jinka ilm ho, ( hurmat Sabit honey) ka hukm nazil hua tha, phir ye ( hukm ( bhi nazil hua tha : panch baar doodh pilaaney se jinka ilm ho."
3599,"abdul-wahaab ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Umra ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna wo keh rahi thin. padhi. (aagey) usi ki tarah (hai.)"
3600,"Amr Naqid aur ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Sehla binte- Suhel (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! main Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar aaney ki bina par (apne shauhar ( abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke chehrey main (tabdeeli) dekhti hun. padhi. halanke wo unka haleef bhi hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey doodh pilaa do. unhon-ne kaha : main usey kaisey doodh pilaaun? jabke wo bada (aadmi) hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : main achi tarah janta hun ke wo bada aadmi hai. Amr ne apni hadis mein ye izafa kya : aur wo (Saalim (Raziallahu anhu)) badr mein Sharik huey they. aur ibne-abi-Umar ki riwayat mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey . (aap ka maqsud ye tha ke kisi bartan mein doodh nikal kar Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ko pilwaa dein.)"
3601,"Ayub ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se, unhon-ne Qasim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Salim (Raziallahu anhu) , abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) aur unki ahliya ke sath unke ghar hi main ( thehre huey) they. to (unki ahliya ( yani (Sehla ( binte-Suhail (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : Salim mardon ki) had ( bulooghat ko pahunch chuka hai aur wo ( aurton ke barey mein) wo sab samajhney laga hai jo wo samajhtey hain aur wo hamarey yahan (ghar mein) aata hai aur main khayal karti hun ke abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke dil mein us se kuchh (na-gawari) hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : tum usey doodh pilaa do, is par haram ho jaogi aur wo ( na-gawari) door ho jaeygi jo abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke dil mein hai. chunanche wo dobara aap ke paas aai aur kaha : maine usey doodh pilwaa diya hai to ( ab ( wo na-gawari door ho gaee jo abu-Huzaifa ke dil mein thi."
3602,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein ibne-abi-Mulaika ne bataya, unhein Qasim-bin-Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr ne khabar di, unhein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke Sehla binte- Suhail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! Saalim. padhi. (unhon-ne) Salim Maula abi Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein (kaha : ). padhi. hamarey sath hamarey ghar mein rehta hai. wo mardon ki had bulooghat ko pahunch chuka hai aur wo (sab kuchh ( jaanney laga hai jo mard jantey hain. aap ne farmaya : tum usey doodh pilaa do to tum is par haraam ho jaogi. (maano ye hukm sirf Hazrat Sehla (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye tha. ( ) ibne-abi-Mulaika ne) kaha : main saal bhar ya iske qareeb thehra, maine ye hadis bayan na ki, main us (ko bayan karne) se darta raha, phir main Qasim se mila to maine unhein kaha : aap ne mujhey aik hadis sunai thi, jo maine iske baad kabhi bayan nahi ki, unhon-ne puchha : wo kon si hadis hai? maine unhein batai, unhon-ne kaha : usey mere hawale se bayan karo ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey uski khabar di thi."
3603,"Shoba ne humaid bin Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Zenab binte- Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : aap ke paas ( ghar mein) aik qareebul-bulooghat ladka aata hai jisey main pasand nahi karti ke wo mere paas aaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya : kya tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki zindagi) main namuna nahi hai? unhon-ne (aagey) kaha : abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ne kaha thi : aey Allah ke rasool! Salim (Raziallahu anhu) mere samney aata hai aur (ab) wo mard hai, aur us wjah se abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke dil mein kuchh na-gawari hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey doodh pilaa do taake wo tumharey paas aa sakey."
3604,"Bukair se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Humaid-bin-Naafe se suna wo keh rahe they, maine Zainab-binte-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahi thin : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se suna wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se keh rahi thin : Allah ki qism ! mere dil ko ye baat achi nahi lagti ke mujhey koi aisa ladka dekhey jo razaat (doodh pilaney) se mustaghni (be-niyaaz) ho chuka hai. unhon-ne puchha : kyon? sahla-binte-Suhail (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai thin, unhon-ne kaha tha : aey Allah ke rasool ! Allah ki qism ! main Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ke) ghar mein) daakhiley ki wjah se abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke chehrey par na-gawari si mehsus karti hon, kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey doodh pilaa do. usne kaha : wo to dadhi wala hai. aap ne farmaya : usey doodh pilaa do, us se wo na-gawari khatm ho jaeygi jo abu-Huzaifa ke chehrey par hai. ( Sehla (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Allah ki qism ! (iske baad) maine abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke chehrey par (kabhii) na-gawari mehsus nahi ki."
3605,"abu-Ubaida-bin-Abdullah-bin-zam'a ne mujhey khabar di ke unki walida Zainab-binte-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke unki walida, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) anhaa kaha karti thin : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tamam beeviyon ne is baat se inkar kiya ke is ( badi umr ki) razaat (doodh pilaney) ki wjah se kisi ko apne ghar mein dakhil honey dein, aur unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham usey mahz rukhsat khayal karti hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khas taur par Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ko di thi, lihaza is ( tarah ki) razaat ki wjah se na koi hamarey paas aaney wala bin sakega aur na hamein dekhney wala."
3606,"abu-Ahwas ne hamein Ash'as se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, aur unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey jabke mere paas aik aadmi betha hua tha. ye baat aap par nagawar guzri , aur maine aap ke chehrey par ghussa dekha, kaha : to maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ye razaat (doodh pilaney) (ke rishtey se) mera bhai hai, kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (tum khawaateen ( apne dudh-sharik bhaiyon (ke mamley ( ko dekh liya karo) achi tarah ghaur kar liya karo) kyonke razaat bhook hi se ( moa'tabar ( hai."
3607,"Shoba , Sufiyan aur Zayda sab ne Ash'as-bin-abu-Shasa se abu-Ahwas ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne ( bhi) (jama'at mein se) ke alfaz kahey ."
3608,"Yazeed-bin-zuraia' ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-abu-Arooba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Khaleel Saleh se, unhon-ne abu-Alqama haashmi se aur unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hunain ke din ( jang mein fateh hasil karne ke baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Autas ki taraf aik lashkar bheja, unka dushman se saamnaa hua. unhon-ne un ( dushmanon ( se ladai ki, phir un par ghalib aagey aur unmein se kaneezein hasil kar lein, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein se kuchh logon ne unke mushrik khaawindon (ki maujoodgii ( ki bina par unse mujamiat (sambhog) karne mein harj mehsus kiya, is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne iske barey mein (ye aayat ( nazil farmai : aur shadi shuda auratein (bhi haram hain) siwaey un ( laundiyon (ke jo (jang ke douraan) tumhari milkiyat mein aa jaye. yani jab unki iddat poori ho jaey to (tumhari laundiyaan bin janey ki bina par) wo tumharey liye halal hain."
3609,"Abdul-Aala ne hamein Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu-Khaleel se riwayat ki ke abu-Alqama haashmi ne hadis bayan ki, unhein Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hunain ke din aik sariya (fouji dasta) bhejaa. padhi. ( aagey ( Yazeed bin Zaree ki hadis ke ham mana hai lekin unhon-ne kaha : siwaey un ( laundiyon (ke jinke Malik tumharey daain hath hon, wo tumharey liye halal hain. aur unhon-ne jab unki iddat poori ho jaey ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye. (is sariya mein jo kaneezein hath aaein ye waqia unke barey mein hai.)"
3610,Shoba ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham-mana hadis bayan ki.
3611,"Shoba ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Khaleel se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Autas ke din sahaba ko laundiyan milin jinke khawind bhi they, is par wo (unse taalluqat, qaaim kartey huey) darey (ke ye gunah na ho ( is par ye aayat nazil ki gaee : aur shadi shuda auratein ( bhi haram hain) siwaey un ( laundiyon (ke jinke tumharey daain hath Malik ho jaaein."
3612,Saeed ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
3613,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-rumeh ne kaha : Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Sad-bin-abi-Waqas aur abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik ladkey ke barey mein jhagdaa kiya. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ye mere bhai Utba-bin-abi-waqaas ka betaa hai, usne mujhey wasiyat ki thi ke ye uska betaa hai, aap uski mushabihat (similarity) dekh lein. abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye mera bhai hai, Allah ke rasool ! ye mere bap ki londi se usi ke bistar par paida hua hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski mushabihat (similarity) dekhi to aap ne waazeh taur par Utba ke sath mushabihat (similarity) ( bhi) mehsus ki, iske baad aap ne farmaya : abd ! ye tumhara (bhai) hai. ( uski wajah ye hai ke) bachcha sahib faraash ka hai, aur zina karne waley ke liye patthar ( naakaamii aur mahroomii ( hai. aur Sauda-binte-Zama ! (tum (us se parda karo. iske baad us ne kabhi Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko nahi dekha aur Muhammad-bin-Rumeh ne aap ke alfaz (ya abd ( zikr nahi kiye."
3614,Sufiyan-bin-Uena aur Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki. lekin Mamar aur ibne-Uena ki hadis mein hai : bachcha sahib faraash ka hai. aur un donon ne ''zaanii ke liye patthar hai'' ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye.
3615,"Mamar ne Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bachcha bistar waley ka hai aur zaanii ke liye patthar ( naakaamii aur mahroomii ( hai."
3616,"Saeed-bin-Mansoor, Zuhair-bin-Harab , Abdul-Aala-bin-Hammad aur Amr Naqid sab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Zohri se khabar di. ibne- Mansoor ne kaha : Saeed ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Abdul-Aala ne kaha : abu-Salma se ya Saeed se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Zuhair ne kaha : Saeed ya abu-Salma ne un donon mein se aik ne ya donon ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. aur Amr ne aik baar kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Zohri ke hawale se Saeed aur abu-Salma se, aur aik baar kaha : Saeed ya abu-Salma se, aur aik baar kaha : Saeed ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. ( aagey ( jis tarah Mamar ki hadis hai."
3617,"Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khush-khush mere paas tashrif laaey, aap ke chehrey ( peshani (ke khutoot chamak rahe they, aap ne farmaya : tum ne dekha nahi ke abhi-abhi ( banu-mudlij ke jiyotish) mujzizz ne Zaid-bin-Haarisa aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha hai, aur kaha hai : un qadmon mein se aik ( qadam ( doosrey mein se hai. (eik betey ka hai, doosra bap ka ("
3618,"Sufiyan ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khush-khush mere paas tashrif laey aur farmaya : Aaisha ! kya tum ne dekha nahi ke mujzizz mudliji mere paas aaya, us ne Usama aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, un donon par aik chadar thi jisne unke saron ko dhaanpaa hua tha aur unke paon nangey they, to usne kaha : bila shubah ye qadam aik doosrey mein se hain."
3619,"Ibrahim-bin-Sad ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik qiyaafa shanaas (jiyotish) aaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi maujood they, Usama-bin-Zaid aur Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) (eik chadar mein) letey huey they, to usne kaha : bila shubah ye qadam aik doosrey mein se hain. us se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khushi hui aur aapko bahut achchha laga, aap ne ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko bhi batai."
3620,"Yunus , Mamar aur ibne-Juraij sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath , un ( Leis , Sufiyan aur Ibrahim-bin-Sad ( ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki aur) ibne- Wahab ne) Yunus ki hadis mein ye izafa kiya : aur mujzizz aik qiyaafa shanas (haath ya shakl dekh kar pehchaan bataney wala) tha."
3621,"Muhammad-bin Abu-Bakar ne Abdul-Malik bin Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se shadi ki to unke yahan teen din qiyam kya aur farmaya : apne ahal ( shauhar (ke nazdeek tumhari qadr w manzilat mein kisi tarah ki kami nahi, agar tum chaho to main tumharey paas (qiyam ke liye) saat (7) din rakh leta hun aur agar maine tumharey yahan saat (7) din qiyam kya to apni saari beeviyon ke yahan saat (7) saat din qiyam karunga."
3622,"Abdullah-bin Abu-Bakar ne Abdul-Malik bin Abu-Bakar se, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya aur wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas thehar gain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha : apne shauhar ke samney tumharey martabey mein koi kami nahi, agar tum chaho to main tumharey yahan saat (7) din qiyam karunga, aur agar tum chaho to teen din qiyam karunga phir ( baari-baari ( sab ke yahan jana shuru karunga . Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya : aap teen din qiyam farmaein."
3623,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne hamein Abdur-Rehman bin humaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdul-Malik bin Abu-Bakar se, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to aap unke paas gaey, iske baad aap ne nikalney ka irada kya to unhon-ne aap ke kapdey ko pakad liya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum chaho to main mazeed tumharey yahan qiyam karunga aur tumharey sath iska hisab rakhunga, kunwari ke liye saat (7) raatein hain aur seba (dohajo) ke liye teen raatein hain."
3624,abu-Zamra ne Abdur-Rehman bin Humaid se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
3625,"abdul-Wahid bin aiman ne Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon ( abdul-Wahid ( ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un (Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha)) se shadi ki, aur bahut si baton ka zikr kya, unmein ye baat bhi thi : aap ne farmaya : agar tum chaho ke main tumharey yahan saat (7) din qiyam karun (to ye ho sakta hai) aur agar maine tumharey yahan saat (7) din qiyam kya to apni saari beeviyon ke yahan saat (7) saat din qiyam karunga."
3626,"Hushaim ne hamein Khalid se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab koi dohajo (seba) ke baad baakara se shadi karey to uske yahan saat (7) din qiyam karey aur jab baakra ke baad kisi seba se shadi karey to iske yahan teen din qiyam kare. Khalid ne kaha : agar main kahun ke unhon-ne usey marfooan bayan kya hai, to main sach kahunga lekin unhon-ne kaha tha : sunnat isi tarah hai. (ye hadis ko marfoo karne ke mutradif hai.)"
3627,"Sufiyan ne Ayub aur Khalid Haza se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : sunnat mein se hai ke (dulha) baakara ke yahan saat (7) raatein qiyam kare. Khalid ne kaha : agar main chaahun to keh sakta hun : unhon-ne usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfooan bayan kya hai."
3628,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nau (9) beeviyan thin, jab aap unmein baari taqseem farmatey to pehli baari wali biwi ke paas naween raat hi pahunchtey. wo sab har raat us (biwi ke) ghar mein jama ho jati thin jahan Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif farma hotey, Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) aaein to aap ne apna hath unki taraf phailaaya. unhon (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) ne kaha : ye Zenab hain aap ne apna hath rok liya, is par un donon mein takraar ho gaee yahan tak ke unki aawaazein buland ho gain, aur (usi doran mein) Namaz ki iqamat ho gaee, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka wahan se guzar hua, unhon-ne unki aawazein sunin to kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap Namaz ke liye tashrif laaiye aur unke munh mein mitti daaliye . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : abhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni Namaz poori karengey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaeingey wo mujhey aisey-aisey (daant-dapat) karengey. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz mukammal ki, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) un (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (ke paas aaey aur unhein sakht sarzanish ki aur kaha : kya tum aisa karti ho?"
3629,"Jarir ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid (Urwa-bin-Zubair) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine koi aurat nahi dekhi jo mujhey Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) ki nisbat zyada pasandida ho ke main iske paikar mein hon (is jaisi bin jaun) aik aisi khatun ki nisbat jin mein kuchh garm mizaaji (bhi) thi, kaha : jab wo boodhi ho gain to unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath apni baari ka din Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko de diya. unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! maine aap ke sath apni baari ka din Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko de diya hai. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko 2 din detey, aik unka din aur aik Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ka din."
3630,"Aqba bin Khalid, Zuhair aur Sharik, un sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) jab boodhi ho gain. aagey Jarir ki hadis ke ham-mana hai aur Sharik ki hadis mein ye izafa hai : wo pehli khatun thin jin se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere baad nikah kya."
3631,"abu-Usama ne hamein Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid (Urwa) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main un aurton par ghairat karti thi jo apne aapko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney bataur hiba pesh karti thin. main kehti : kya koi aurat bhi khud ko hiba kar sakti hai? jab Allah Taala ne nazil farmaya : aap un aurton mein se jisey chaahein peechhey kar dein aur jisey chaahein apne paas jagah dein aur jisey aap ne alag kar diya tha unmein se bhi jisey aap ka dil chahey laaein. kaha : to maine kaha : Allah ki qasam! main aap ke rab ko nahi dekhti magar wo aap ke liye aap ki khahish (ko pura karne) mein jaldi karta hai."
3632,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, wo kaha karti thin : kya us aurat ko haya mehsus nahi hoti jo khud ko kisi mard ke liye hiba karti hai. yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne ye nazil farmaya : aap un aurton mein se jisey chaahein peechhey karein aur jisey chaahein apne paas jagah dein. to maine kaha : bila shubah aap ka rab aap ki khahish (ko pura karne) mein jaldi karta hai."
3633,"Muhammad-bin-Bakr ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Ata ne khabar di, kaha : sirf ke maqam par ham Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke janazey mein hazir huey to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya hain. jab tum unki charpai uthao to usko idhar-udhar harkat na dena, na hilaanaa, narmi (aur ehtiraam) se kaam lena, Amr waaqe ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nau (9) beeviyan thin, aap aath (8) ke liye baari taqseem kartey aur aik ke liye taqseem na kartey they. Ata ne kaha : jinko aap baari nahi detey they wo Hazrat Safiya-binte-Huyi bin akhtab (Raziallahu anhu) thin."
3634,"Abdur-Razzaq ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur ye izafa kya ke Ata ne kaha : wo un sab mein se, aakhir mein faut honey wali (Memuna (Raziallahu anha)) thin, wo Madina mein faut huin."
3635,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : aurat ke sath char baton ki bina par shadi ki jati hai : uske maal ki wjah se, uske hasab (w nasab) ki wjah se, uski khoobsoorti ki wjah se aur uske Deen ki wjah se. tum Deen wali ke sath (shadi karke) kaamyab bano. tumharey hath khaak aalud hon. (ye is baat se kinaaya hai ke tum hamesha kaam kartey raho. ("
3636,"Ata se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein aik aurat se shadi ki, meri mulaqat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hui to aap ne puchha : Jaabir! tum ne nikah kar liya hai? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne farmaya : kunwari hai ya dohajo (shauhar deeda)? maine kaha : dohajo. aap ne farmaya : baakra se kyon na ki, tum us se dil lagi kartey? maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! meri bahnein hain to main dara ke wo mere aur unke darmyan haail ho jaeygi, aap ne farmaya : phir theek hai, bila shubah kisi aurat se shadi (main raghbat ( uske Deen , maal aur khoobsoorti ki wjah se ki jati hai, tum Deen wali ko chuno tumharey hath khaak aalud hon."
3637,"Shoba ne hamein Maharib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine aik aurat se shadi ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : kya tum ne nikah kya hai? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne puchha : kunwari se ya dohajo (seba) se? maine kaha : dohajo se. aap ne farmaya : tum kunwaariyon aur unki mulaaibat ( aapasii khel kood ( se ( door) kahan reh gaey ? Shoba ne kaha : maine ye hadis Amr-bin-Dinar ke samney bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha : maine ye hadis Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suni thi aur unhon-ne kaha tha : tum ne kunwari se ( shadi ( kyon na ki? tum uske sath kheltey wo tumharey sath khelti."
3638,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur abu Rabe Zahrani ne hamein hadis bayan ki, Yahya ne kaha : Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Amr-bin-Dinar se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke (mere walid) Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne wafat paai aur peechhey nau (9) betiyaan. padhi. ya kaha : saat (7) betiyaan chhodin, to maine aik dohajo aurat se nikah kar liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : Jaabir ! nikah kar liya hai? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne puchha : kunwari hai ya dohajo? maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! dohajo hai. aap ne farmaya : kunwari kyon nahi, tum us se dil lagi kartey, wo tum se dil lagi karti. padhi. ya farmaya : tum uske sath hanstey kheltey , wo tumharey sath hansti khelti. padhi. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : ( mere walid ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne wafat paai aur peechhey nau (9) . padhi. ya saat (7) . padhi. betiyan chhodin, to maine achchha na samjha ke main unke paas unhi jaisi (kam Umr) ley aaoon. maine chaha ke aisi aurat laaun jo unki nigehdaasht karey aur unki islaah kare. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah tumhen barkat de! ya aap ne mere liye khair aur bhalai ki dua farmai aur abu-Rabe ki riwayat mein hai : tum iske sath dil lagi kartey wo tumharey sath dil lagi karti aur tum uske sath hanstey-kheltey, wo tumharey sath hansti khelti."
3639,"Sufiyan ne hamein Amr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : Jaabir! kya tum ne nikah kar liya hai? aur aagey yahan tak bayan kya : aisi aurat jo unki nigehdasht karey aur unki kanghi karey, aap ne farmaya : tum ne theek kya aur unhon-ne iske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kya."
3640,"Shabi ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik ghazwey mein Sharik they. jab ham wapas huey to maine apne sust raftar oont ko thoda sa tez kya, mere sath peechhey se aik sawar aa kar mila unhon-ne lohey ki nauk wali chhadi se jo unke sath thi, mere oont ko kachoka lagaya, to wo itna tez chalney laga jitna aap ne kisi behtreen oont ko) tez chaltey huey) dekha, aap ne puchha : Jaabir ! tumhen kis cheez ne jaldi mein daal rakha hai? maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine nai-nai shadi ki hai. aap ne puchha : baakara se shadi ki hai ya dohajo se? unhon-ne kaha : dohajo se. aap ne farmaya : tum ne kisi (kunwari) ladki se kyon na ki, tum uske sath dil-lagi kartey, wo tumharey sath dil lagi karti? kaha : jab ham Madina aaey, (us mein) dakhil honey lagey to aap ne farmaya : thehar jao, ham raat. padhi. yani isha. padhi. ke waqt dakhil hon, taake bikhrey huey baalon wali baal sanwaar ley aur jis jiska shauhar ghayab raha, wo baal (wghaira) saaf kar ley. aur farmaya : jab ghar pahunchna to aql w tahammul se kaam lena (haalate-haiz mein hambistari na karna.)"
3641,"Wahab bin kaisaan ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik ghazwey mein nikla tha, mere oont ne meri raftaar sust kar di to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif ley aaey aur farmaya : Jaabir ! maine kaha : ji . aap ne puchha : kya mamla hai? maine kaha : mere liye mera oont sust pad chuka hai aur thak gaya hai, isliye main peechhey reh gaya hun. aap (apni sawari se) utrey aur apni mudey huey sirey wali chhadi se usey kachokaa lagaya, phir farmaya : Sawar ho jao. main Sawar ho gaya. iske baad maine khud ko dekha ke main usko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki ontni) se (aagey badhney se) rok raha hun. phir aap ne puchha : kya tum ne shadi kar li? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne puchha : kunwari se ya dohajo se? maine kaha : dohajo hai. aap ne farmaya : (kunwari) ladki se kyon na ki, tum uske sath dil lagi kartey, wo tumharey sath dil lagi karti. maine kaha : meri (chhoti) behnein hain. maine chaha ke aisi aurat se shadi karun jo unki dhaaras bandhaaey, unki kanghi karey aur unki nigehdasht kare. aap ne farmaya : tum ( ghar) pahunchne waley ho, jab pahunch jao to ehtiyat aur aql mandi se kaam lena. phir puchha : kya tum apna oont bechogey? maine kaha : ji haan, chunanche aap ne wo ( oont ( mujh se aik auqiya ( chandi ki qeemat ( mein khareed liya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahunch gaey aur main subah ke waqt pahuncha , masjid mein aaya to aapko masjid ke darwazey par paya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : abhi pahunchey ho? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne farmaya : apna oont chhodo aur masjid mein ja kar do rakaat Namaz ada karo. main masjid mein dakhil hua, Namaz padhi, phir (aap ke paas) wapas aaya to aap ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke mere liye aik auqiya ( chandi ( tol dein, chunanche Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne wazan kya, aur tarazu ko jhukaya (auqiya se zyada tolaa) kaha : iske baad mein chal pada, jab maine peeth pheri to aap ne farmaya : Jaabir ko mere paas bulao . mujhey bulaya gaya. maine (dil mein) kaha : ab aap mera oont ( bhi) mujhey wapas kar dengey aur mujhey koi cheez us se zyada na-pasand na thi (ke main qeemat wsool karne ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apna oont bhi wapas le loon.) aap ne farmaya : apna oont ley lo aur uski qeemat bhi tumhari hai."
3642,"abu-Nazara ne hamein Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they, aur main aik pani dhoney waley oont par) sawar ( tha aur wo peechhey reh janey waley logon ke sath tha. kaha : aap ne usey . padhi. mera khayal hai, unhon-ne kaha : apne paas maujood kisi cheez se maara, ya kaha : kachokaa lagaya. kaha : iske baad wo logon (ke oonton ( se aagey nikalney laga, wo mujh se kheencha-tani karne laga yahan tak ke mujhey usko rokna padta tha. kaha : iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mujhey ye itney-itney mein bechogey? Allah tumhen maaf farmaey! kaha : maine arz ki. Allah ke Nabi! wo aap hi ka hai. aap ne (dobara) puchha : kya tum mujhey wo itney itney mein bechogey? Allah tumharey gunah maaf farmaai ! kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke Nabi ! wo aap ka hai. kaha : aur aap ne mujh se (ye bhi) puchha : kya apne walid (ki wafat (ke baad tum ne nikah kar liya hai? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne puchha : dohajo (shauhar deeda ( se ya doshiza (kunwari ladki) se? maine kaha : dohajo se. aap ne farmaya : tum ne kunwari se kyon na shadi ki, wo tumharey sath hansti khelti aur tum uske sath hanstey kheltey aur wo tumharey sath dil lagi karti, tum iske sath dil lagi kartey ? abu-Nazara ne kaha : ye aisa kalima tha jisey musalman (muhawaratan) kehtey they ke aisey-aisey karo, Allah tumharey gunah bakhsh de."
3643,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aurat ko pasli se paida kya gaya hai, wo tumharey liye kisi aik tareeqey par hargiz seedhi nahi reh sakti, agar tum us se fayda uthana chaho to (usi tarah) fayda utha logey ke usmein tedh rahegi aur agar tum usey seedha karne chalogey to usey tod dalogey, aur usey todna uski talaaq hai."
3644,"abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo Allah aur qiyamat ke din par eman rakhta hai jab (apni biwi mein) koi ( pasand na aaney wala ( mamla dekhey to achi tarah se baat kahey ya khamosh rahe aur aurton ke sath achchhey sulook ki nasihat qabool karo kyonke aurat pasli se paida ki gaee hai. aur pasliyon mein sabse zyada tedh uske uper waley hissey mein hai. agar tum usey seedha karne lag jaogey to usey tod doge aur agar chhod doge to wo tedhi hi rahegi, aurton ke sath achchhey sulook ki nasihat qabool karo."
3645,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdul-Hameed bin Jafar ne Imran bin abi Anas se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Umar-bin Hakam se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi momin mard kisi momina aurat se bughz na rakhey. agar usey uski koi aadat na-pasand hai to dusri pasand hogi. ya aap ne (iske siwa koi aur) farmaya."
3646,"abu-Aasim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abdul-hameed bin Jafar ne pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. usi ki tarah."
3647,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Yunus ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : agar Hawa (Alaihissalam) na hotin to koi aurat apne shauhar se kabhi khayanat na karti."
3648,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin, unmein aik ye thi : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar Bani-Israeel na hotey to khana kharab na hota aur gosht badbudar na hota aur agar hawa (Alaihissalam) na hotin to koi aurat apne shauhar se khayanat na karti."
3649,Saiyedna Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' duniya kaam nikalney ki cheez hai aur behtar kaam nikalney ki cheez duniya mein nek aurat hai.''
3650,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey ibne-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah aurat pasli ki tarah hai, agar tum usey seedha karne lag jaogey to usey tod dalogey aur agar usey chhod doge to us se fayda uthaogey jabke usmein tedhaapan (maujood) hoga."
3651,Zohri ke bhatijey ne apne chacha (Zohri ( se isi sanad ke sath bilkul usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
